  "title": "Car Wrap - (PPF/Wrap/Film Installer)  汽车贴膜",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>5.5-day work week</strong></em></p><p>五天班工作制</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Provide expertise in installing Car Body Wrapping, Protective film wrapping (PPF), and Tinted film</li><li>Duties include cleaning the car before any installation, fixing the decals or wraps in the proper place, and ensuring they are secure.</li><li>Experience in operating large-format printers</li><li>Ensure that the workstation is well-maintained before and after each job.</li><li>Execute any other tasks as required by the supervisor</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min 2 to 5 years of relevant work experience.</li><li>Meticulous, strong follow-up, attention to detail.</li><li>Good interpersonal, motivated, and positive attitude</li><li>Good knowledge of tools and equipment.</li></ul><p>Workplace in Sin Ming/ Bishan region<br />To apply for this job, contact WhatsApp at 96788908  </p><p><strong>职责和需要</strong></p><p>• 具备汽车车身贴膜,保护膜(PPF),有色膜,和贴膜的安装专业知识</p><p>• 工作职责包括在任何安装之前的汽车清洁，确保贴纸，贴膜牢固稳定并且位置正确</p><p>• 有操作大幅打印机的经验</p><p>• 并确保其工作之前和之后保持良好状态</p><p>• 至少有 2 到 5 年相关工作经</p><p>• 执行主管要求的其他任务</p><p>工作位于新明/碧山地区<br />有意申请这份工作者，请联系 WhatsApp  96788908  </p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
